{"tid":726334,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4 pro club] D1 球會招翼 x 1 及GK x 1踢VPL S19 金盃淘汰賽及HKEFPCL","createTime":"2018-07-02T09:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T14:41:59.000Z","uid":78671,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa9faf686ebd1326557304e16e4ad24e561dada","tid":726334,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"球隊因賽制問題缺席了上季HKVPL S18 賽事，今季已報名參加HKVPL S19 &amp; HKEFPCL 電競聯賽 S2 賽事<br />\n<br />\n長遠目標係挑戰傳統勁旅，故希望能吸納更多好波之人。<br />\n<br />\n現招以下位置好手補強（翼x1、龍門x1），希望一齊夾好波。<br />\n<br />\n踢法：理想係打造一支踢法上模仿巴塞或曼城的傳控球隊，故球隊希望球員有在隊友旁邊現位（形成三角形）幫波的意識，及中前場球員必須擁有高控球能力（有能力在極短時間內猜散強隊在比賽時的高壓迫搶，比人迫兩下就甩波or 傳球失誤便不了）<br />\n不是單純踢跑狗反擊/高q大棍燒味，目標係要踢出有球隊特色及技術的踢法。希望能邀到有共同理念及能力的選手一齊合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每晚10點左右進行試腳。<br />\n<br />\n如有意試腳，請add telegram <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ps4fifa_pro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fps4fifa_pro&d=wJQDztqai%2BickeFlznggjdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a6be1e4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ps4fifa_pro</a><br />\n<br />\nthanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb7f3e43d0f3a0269ee72b92e9722a19ad6ae11","tid":726334,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"今晚9pm 有場，歡迎加tg 試腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa68e22590f126ebe1c1668c4208bc050298885","tid":726334,"uid":107755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeb7f3e43d0f3a0269ee72b92e9722a19ad6ae11","tid":726334,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"今晚9pm 有場，歡迎加tg 試腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T14:41:59.000Z","msg":"防中想試 lukkompany1992 psn"}]}